      <title>Ubuntu添加vscode源</title>
      <link>https://leejoker.top/post/ubuntu%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0vscode%E6%BA%90/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Mar 2021 10:29:00 +0800</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://leejoker.top/post/ubuntu%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0vscode%E6%BA%90/</guid>
      <description>&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;添加apt源到/etc/apt/sources.list文件&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-shell&#34;&gt;$ sudo echo &amp;quot;deb [arch=amd64] http://packages.microsoft.com/repos/vscode stable main&amp;quot; &amp;gt;&amp;gt; /etc/apt/sources.list
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;添加gpg公钥&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-shell&#34;&gt;$ sudo curl https://packages.microsoft.com/keys/microsoft.asc | gpg --dearmor &amp;gt; /etc/apt/trusted.gpg.d/microsoft.gpg
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
